snippet.title: Steam 「Shikhondo: Youkai Rampage」 Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
#cfk #steam #Shikhondo

Seal away the youkais that have escaped from hell!
Avoid the dazzling spread of bullets, and stand up to the 「Youkai Rampage」!

A girl falls into the world unknown, losing even the memory of her name.
In the world full of soul-starved youkais, she meets the Grim Reaper
and begins the harrowing journey in search of her memories and her family.

Will she be able to find her memory, her hometown and her family?

● 「Shikhondo: Youkai Rampage」 Steam store page
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2712480/Shikhondo_Youkai_Rampage/
